After months upon months of working on this, redrawing panels, making character designs, storyboarding dialogue, getting crit, starting over, starting over again, and finally feeling satisfied with this post enough to post it, I am now officially done with my SCP that is a sentient webcomic.

Sorry that I didn't post it during Pride month since every one of the characters is LGBT in some way.

Thanks to GibberingEloquence for crit!

And a special thank you to Rimple for giving me the ideas of Cayde Callion the trans punk rock zombie and Jym Daephys, the basketball fairy.

I really hope you all enjoy!





